{"tid":1312530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察Facebook公開發佈血腥暴力性質圖片","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:34:42.000Z","uid":213552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c68f59c5174fe90e34515d3b6cc68b7a1c60bb7","tid":1312530,"uid":213552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責香港警察刻意公開發佈血腥暴力性質圖片行為，並強調會對所有禁止發佈的內容舉報帖子，追究到底。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 社群守則<br />\n<br />\n12. 暴力與血腥露骨的內容<br />\n政策宗旨<br />\n宣揚暴力、讚揚折磨或羞辱他人的內容可能會營造出讓人望之卻步的環境，因此會遭到移除。我們允許透過暴力畫面（但有某些限制）提高他人對此類議題的重視。我們瞭解人們重視討論重要議題（例如人權濫用或恐怖主義行為）的權利。此外，我們也瞭解人們對於血腥暴力內容的觀感不一。有鑑於此，我們特別針對血腥或暴力內容新增了一個警告標籤，除了讓這類內容無法接觸到未滿 18 歲的人士，還要讓用戶在點擊並觀看之前，事先知道該內容屬於血腥暴力性質。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/HongKongPoliceForce/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=2482149038539712&amp;__xts__%5B0%5D=68.ARCzrlD-Hpf-Qs17Vvgs_nfR2lMTBATJa_xORHJDYlgq54nUNioWHWMXuCmiL7ivUhIS988aEo7ma12Tskf3lx9aIsuGM-E6UMGmutJWqqc9Cg02e3YNGCf6EY916T9VgVUD78mhIoZ8GKawSAHwyFXJR_41OsQ3SoOsICe1kpKIkJiHQg2Hg2pmStWoMzJoILuvHDPmFG7VObzfbi_yb0dGTQjewA99Qn8-H3TejbDL2hkpmSOMxbiwoTLbRooP7xp1f6O-1_SecEB_qzOzI9TIxvox5mfACDgKsL2hWbSbN-nqJZBMftXcObd9Zy2XUQuLcYrjYVuagDF-LMFhNpe9pMktGtLzbdm_OqeHVuLe241r4nLP4gKcdpOeCtsbm2X-nciq6sRb3qN60qf6uBI48T_EhjscAKwccWgbRvO3_cxc3mIIwuH4obQmOokz3cg58qKN1h5mDHxQTDnD&amp;__tn__=-UC-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2Fphotos%2F%3Ftab%3Dalbum%26album_id%3D2482149038539712%26__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARCzrlD-Hpf-Qs17Vvgs_nfR2lMTBATJa_xORHJDYlgq54nUNioWHWMXuCmiL7ivUhIS988aEo7ma12Tskf3lx9aIsuGM-E6UMGmutJWqqc9Cg02e3YNGCf6EY916T9VgVUD78mhIoZ8GKawSAHwyFXJR_41OsQ3SoOsICe1kpKIkJiHQg2Hg2pmStWoMzJoILuvHDPmFG7VObzfbi_yb0dGTQjewA99Qn8-H3TejbDL2hkpmSOMxbiwoTLbRooP7xp1f6O-1_SecEB_qzOzI9TIxvox5mfACDgKsL2hWbSbN-nqJZBMftXcObd9Zy2XUQuLcYrjYVuagDF-LMFhNpe9pMktGtLzbdm_OqeHVuLe241r4nLP4gKcdpOeCtsbm2X-nciq6sRb3qN60qf6uBI48T_EhjscAKwccWgbRvO3_cxc3mIIwuH4obQmOokz3cg58qKN1h5mDHxQTDnD%26_